### ============================================================
### HASHMICRO HIRING TEST - COMPLETE MANUAL TEST FILE
### ============================================================
### Cara pakai:
###   1. Buka file ini di VS Code (install extension "REST Client")
###   2. Start server: npm run dev
###   3. Jalankan request satu per satu dari atas ke bawah
###   4. Copy token dari response Login ke variable @token di bawah
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_FROM_LOGIN_RESPONSE_HERE

### ============================================================
### 1. AUTH - REGISTER
### ============================================================

### TC-1.1 Register user baru - berhasil
### Expected: 201 Created, response berisi username & name
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Administrator"
}

### TC-1.2 Register user yang sudah ada - gagal duplicate
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, "Username already exists"
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Administrator"
}

### TC-1.3 Register tanpa username - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Test"
}

### TC-1.4 Register password terlalu pendek (<6) - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, "Password must be at least 6 characters"
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user2",
  "password": "123",
  "name": "Short Password"
}

### TC-1.5 Register username terlalu pendek (<3) - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, "Username must be at least 3 characters"
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Short Username"
}

### ============================================================
### 2. AUTH - LOGIN
### ============================================================

### TC-2.1 Login berhasil - dapat token
### Expected: 200 OK, response berisi data user + token
### *** COPY TOKEN DARI RESPONSE KE @token DI ATAS ***
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### TC-2.2 Login password salah - gagal
### Expected: 401 Unauthorized, "Invalid username or password"
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### TC-2.3 Login username tidak ada - gagal
### Expected: 401 Unauthorized, "Invalid username or password"
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "password123"
}

### TC-2.4 Login tanpa field - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin"
}

### ============================================================
### 3. USER - GET CURRENT (Protected)
### ============================================================

### TC-3.1 Get current user - berhasil
### Expected: 200 OK, response berisi username & name
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/current
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}

### TC-3.2 Get current user tanpa token - gagal
### Expected: 401 Unauthorized, "Token is required"
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/current

### TC-3.3 Get current user token salah - gagal
### Expected: 401 Unauthorized, "Invalid token"
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/current
X-API-TOKEN: invalid-token-here

