### ============================================================
### 10. CHARACTER ANALYSIS - Soal HashMicro
### ============================================================

### TC-10.1 SOAL CASE 1 - Sensitive Case
### Input1: "ABBCD" (5 karakter)
### Input2: "Gallant Duck"
### Karakter unique ABBCD: A, B, C, D (4 unique)
### Sensitive: hanya 'D' yang ada di "Gallant Duck"
### Expected: 1/5 = 20%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "ABBCD",
  "input2": "Gallant Duck",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.2 SOAL CASE 2 - Non-Sensitive Case
### Input1: "ABBCD" (5 karakter)
### Input2: "Gallant Duck"
### Insensitive: 'A' (a), 'C' (c), 'D' (D) ada di "Gallant Duck"
### 'B' (b) TIDAK ada di "Gallant Duck"
### Expected: 3/5 = 60%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "ABBCD",
  "input2": "Gallant Duck",
  "case_type": "insensitive"
}

### TC-10.3 Analysis - Semua karakter match (sensitive)
### Input1: "HELLO" → unique: H, E, L, O
### Input2: "HELLO WORLD"
### Sensitive: H, E, L, O semua ada
### Expected: 4/5 = 80%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "HELLO",
  "input2": "HELLO WORLD",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.4 Analysis - Tidak ada yang match
### Input1: "XYZ"
### Input2: "Hello World"
### Sensitive: X, Y, Z tidak ada di "Hello World"
### Expected: 0/3 = 0%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "XYZ",
  "input2": "Hello World",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.5 Analysis - Case berbeda sensitive vs insensitive
### Input1: "abc"
### Input2: "ABC"
### Sensitive: a≠A, b≠B, c≠C → 0/3 = 0%
### Expected: 0%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "abc",
  "input2": "ABC",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.6 Analysis - Case berbeda insensitive
### Input1: "abc"
### Input2: "ABC"
### Insensitive: a=A, b=B, c=C → 3/3 = 100%
### Expected: 100%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "abc",
  "input2": "ABC",
  "case_type": "insensitive"
}

### TC-10.7 Analysis - Input1 kosong - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, "Input 1 is required"
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "",
  "input2": "Hello",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.8 Analysis - Case type invalid - gagal validasi
### Expected: 400 Bad Request, "Case type must be 'sensitive' or 'insensitive'"
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "ABC",
  "input2": "Hello",
  "case_type": "invalid"
}

### TC-10.9 Analysis - Karakter dengan spasi dan simbol
### Input1: "A@B C"
### Input2: "a@b c test"
### Insensitive: A=a, @=@, B=b, space=space, C=c → semua match
### Expected: 5/5 = 100%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "A@B C",
  "input2": "a@b c test",
  "case_type": "insensitive"
}

### TC-10.10 Analysis - Angka sebagai karakter
### Input1: "123"
### Input2: "a1b2c3"
### Sensitive: 1, 2, 3 semua ada
### Expected: 3/3 = 100%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "123",
  "input2": "a1b2c3",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.11 Analysis - Duplicate chars di input1
### Input1: "AAA" (3 karakter, 1 unique: A)
### Input2: "Apple"
### Sensitive: A ada di "Apple"
### Expected: 1/3 = 33% (dibulatkan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "AAA",
  "input2": "Apple",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

### TC-10.12 Analysis - Input2 lebih pendek dari input1
### Input1: "ABCDE"
### Input2: "A"
### Sensitive: hanya A match
### Expected: 1/5 = 20%
POST {{baseUrl}}/analysis
X-API-TOKEN: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input1": "ABCDE",
  "input2": "A",
  "case_type": "sensitive"
}

